# Frontend Scope

When the user is working on files in **frontend/** (Next.js, React, components, i18n, etc.):

- Delegate to the **ondm-frontend-developer** subagent
- Invoke with: `/ondm-frontend-developer` or "Use the ondm-frontend-developer to..."

The frontend developer works exclusively in `frontend/` and handles:
- Next.js pages and App Router
- React components
- Internationalization (EN/AR)
- Tailwind styling
- Dashboard UI
- API consumption
